    <detaileddescription>
<para>The <bold>IADLXDisplayVariBright1</bold> interface configures Vari-Bright Scaling settings on a display.</para>
<para><table rows="4" cols="2"><row>
<entry thead="no"><para>InterfaceId:</para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>IADLXDisplayVariBright1</para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para>Smart Pointer Interface Name:</para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>IADLXDisplayVariBright1Ptr</para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para>Inherits:</para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para><ref refid="_d_o_x__i_a_d_l_x_display_vari_bright" kindref="compound">IADLXDisplayVariBright</ref></para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para>Inherited By:</para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>N/A</para>
</entry></row>
</table>
</para>
<para>Vari-Bright Scaling adjusts Vari-Bright levels or strength subtly depending on system state and user preferences. The <bold>IADLXDisplayVariBright1</bold> interface is obtained from the <ref refid="_d_o_x__i_a_d_l_x_display_vari_bright" kindref="compound">IADLXDisplayVariBright</ref> interface using <ref refid="_d_o_x__i_a_d_l_x_interface__query_interface" kindref="compound">QueryInterface</ref>.<linebreak/>
</para>
